===Search for the materials left by Anaxa{{subst:void|<!--104030306-->}}===
{{Mission Description|type=trailblaze|location="Murmuring Woods" Grove of Epiphany|update|Head to the Library of Philia with Hyacine to collect materials for the data bank and expand our understanding of Amphoreus.<br />Look for documents related to Anaxagoras.}}
